mmj.transforms

Class GenProofStepStmt

  • java.lang.Object
    • mmj.transforms.GenProofStepStmt

  • public class GenProofStepStmt
extends java.lang.Object
    This class describes generalized proof step statement. In simple cases it is simple proof step statement. But it can be used also to describe statements with implications prefix. Such statements have form "ph -> core" where ph is a prefix which could be used in transformations. The main goal is to support auto-transformations for cases like next example:

    ph -> x in RR ph -> y in RR x + y = z so y + x = z

    Note: simple proof statements also could have form "ph -> core".
